  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250220/extras/e219931dfea65293dbe55fd1f3478d65.avif?t=1697152188\" width=620 height=208 /></span><br>Fallen Region is a third-person survival sandbox game in an open, post-apocalyptic world and extensive gaming capabilities. The game immerses you in a realistic gaming environment saturated with the atmosphere of the post-apocalypse. In the world there are various NPCs such as zombies, military, animals. Different types of weapons are available for battle. The game also has craft and building. Level up your character to get more opportunities!",
